name: 20434 users in hic et nunc
description: This OBJKT celebrates that we are now more than 20000 users in hic et nunc. Each user is represented by a particle that flows down and aggregates to other users. The structure grows organically, like the H=N community. If you ever minted or collected an OBJKT, you should see a particle surrounded by a blue circle. That's you! Click on any particle to see the user information. Type the letter "c" to change between different color modes.
